// *************************************************************************
// *                                                                       *
// * W3ESXi - A module for WHMCS 5 & 4 to manage VMs on Vmware ESXi/ESX    *
// * Release Date: 27 Jul 2012                                             *
// * Version 0.7.5                                                         *
// *                                                                       *
// *************************************************************************
// *************************************************************************
// *                                INSTALLATION                           *
// *************************************************************************
// *                                                                       *
// * 1. Put `whmcs` folder in root of WHMCS on your server. 			   *
// * 2. put contents of `_CSS/clientarea_add_css_to_your_template.txt` in  * 
// *	style file of your template and put `images` folder in  folder  of * 
// *	style file.														   *
// * 3. now on whmcs admin panel,  go  to  setup  menu  and select `addon` *
// *	module then active `w3esxi_admin`.								   *
// *************************************************************************